{"tid":930316,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老幾時死　咪撚累9人【單車大叔車前照過路】","createTime":"2018-12-06T08:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T10:36:03.000Z","uid":225464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c70360e5b40c8737a94d71c150a363bd3f1fd608","tid":930316,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181206/bkn-20181206160045569-1206_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181206%2Fbkn-20181206160045569-1206_00822_001.html&d=xfoDiEkTl4ylQGsgb%2F9wvfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=f6d301ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181206/bkn-20181206160045569-1206_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CyvhjhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCyvhjhG.jpg&h=76413f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>單車大叔無懼綠燈　車前照過路　網民勸勿累人</strong>.<br />\n<br />\n不時有人在馬路上踩單車，但亦應遵守交通規則。近日大埔有大叔突然在馬路燈號轉綠時，踩出馬路，嚇得一眾車輛紛紛急停。<br />\n<br />\n據Facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」的貼文指，星期四（6日）上午約7時許，當時不少車輛正停於大埔太和路與寶雅路交界的路口等待燈號。當綠燈一轉時，車輛齊齊起步，誰知右線一輛貨車與中線的Van仔相繼急煞。<br />\n<br />\n原來有大叔突然在大埔公路大窩段衝出，橫越幾條行車線過路。身處左線的片主亦頓時響按停車，大叔聞聲停下，點頭向片主表示歉意後，便徐徐離去。<br />\n<br />\n發貼者在貼文指，幸好當時留意到旁邊的Van仔停下，否則可能已撞倒大叔。他希望有認識大叔的網民能勸止其舉措，以免累己累人。"},{"pid":"4692ffbecd58490b0d942e688176176a73437603","tid":930316,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"單車冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d69a3c98f42c524aefa3620c1bc7951d339c9a","tid":930316,"uid":22137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"其實人愈大愈怕死 點解啲廢老可以咁撚勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488a2e587aa2bb8370f123b6dfdb8fb2568ddade","tid":930316,"uid":25560,"like":0,"disl